'''Planet Dreams, Incorporated''', also called '''PlanetDreams, Inc.''' was a company specializing in creating inhabitable environments by [[Terraforming/Legends|planetscaping]] asteroids or inhospitable worlds with domes and other technology. The company had several chains in the galaxy, mostly centered around asteroid belts in the [[Mestra system/Legends|Mestra system]] and [[Oseon system/Legends|Oseon]],<ref name="GG3">[[Galaxy Guide 3: The Empire Strikes Back (Second Edition)|''Galaxy Guide 3: The Empire Strikes Back'', Second Edition]]</ref> also including worlds throughout the [[Greater Javin/Legends|Greater Javin]]. Its clients tended to be affluent beings including the [[House of Tagge/Legends|Tagge family]] and [[Lynciro Corporation|Lynciro Corp]].<ref name="Rough">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20040325adv|text=Rough and Tundra|int=Rough and Tundra}}</ref>

==History==
In approximately [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]], the company was owned by three equal partners — [[Treva Horme]], [[Wiorkettle]], and [[Ozz (Ugnaught)/Legends|Ozz]] — who relocated their head offices to [[Bespin/Legends|Bespin's]] [[Cloud City/Legends|Cloud City]].<ref name="GG3" /> They were also planning to open a satellite office in the [[Tingel Arm/Legends|Tingel Arm]].<ref name="Rough" />

The Planet Dreams partners were considering selling private hovering platforms in Bespin's [[Life Zone/Legends|Life Zone]] when Ozz revealed that someone was embezzling money and terraforming equipment from the company. Ozz vowed to investigate but was interrupted in [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]] when the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] arrived and [[Occupation of Bespin|took control]] of the city. The partners decided to download all of their files and evacuate, but while Horme and Wiorkettle followed the plan, Ozz disappeared. The remaining partners moved back to the [[Oseon asteroid belt]] after fleeing Bespin.<ref name="GG3" />

By [[43 ABY]], [[Cix Trouvee]] had become the vice president of the company, a title which he held until his [[Death/Legends|death]] that year.
